listDD = []
	#listDD.append({'value':'Sin Orden','label':'Sin Orden'})
	eqPath = value
	date = system.date.setTime(system.date.addDays(system.date.now(),-1),0,0,0)
	woName = "*"	
	woFilter = system.mes.workorder.createMESWorkOrderFilter()
	woFilter.setWorkOrderNameFilter(woName)
	woFilter.setClosedBeginDate(date)
	woFilter.setEquipmentPathFilter(eqPath)
	results = system.mes.workorder.getMESWorkOrders(woFilter)
	
	for result in results:
		temp = {'Siguiente:':result.getName()}
		listDD.append(temp)
	
	if len(listDD) == 0:
		listDD.append({'Siguiente:':'Sin Orden'})
	return listDD
